^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|A couple of important things to remember here. The most important is "support with support." With 4 hearts, Toots must make some kind of raise, which she did. The next thing to remember is, even if you play limit raises, as opposed to Bergen Raises, you still should play cue bids in competition to show a limit raise. 3H bid by Toots is a weak jump raise, showing less than a limit raise and 4 card support.|
