cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Bergen Raises only apply when your partner opens and the next person passes. Bergen Raises do not apply when you overcall. However, in a lesson I am giving soon, I will be talking about some extensions to Bergen Raises, where you can play them in competition.|
