NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Now I think I scared Cheryl by telling her she was a bit too aggressive before. I think there are at least 2 better bids Cheryl can make than pass. Double is a reasonable bid, showing a real diamond suit. I also think, despite the vulnerability, with such nice distribution and suit, 3D is a reasonable alternative.|
