NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Vered made the correct lead, even if you play top of nothing. When you have not supported partner's suit, you should lead counta low diamond to show 3 is correct by Vered.  Had Vered supported diamonds, showing 3 or more, she should lead the ten as top of nothing.|
